# The site itself is a static Astro build and needs no environment variables.
#
# The contact form's Turnstile SITE key is public and lives in source
# (src/config/site.ts, `turnstileSiteKey`) — not here.
#
# Contact-form email delivery is handled by a separate Cloudflare Worker in
# workers/contact-form/. Its secrets (TURNSTILE_SECRET, DEST_EMAIL) are set with
# `wrangler secret put`, and for local Worker development go in
# workers/contact-form/.dev.vars (gitignored). See workers/contact-form/README.md.
